   :author: Rachel Reyes
   :difficulty: 1.0
   :basecourse: csawesome
   :topic: Unit3-If-Statements/Exercises
   :from_source: F
   :answer_a: x = 0;
   :answer_b: x >= 0;
   :answer_c: if (x > 5) x += 2; else x = 0;
   :answer_d: if (x < 2) x = 0; else x += 2;
   :answer_e: None of the above
   :correct: e

   Which of the following is equivalent to the code segment below?

   .. code-block:: java

    if ( x > 5 ) x = x + 2;
    if ( x >= 2 ) x = 0;